messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to repent of all sexual sins I have been involved with I renounce those sins lust fornication adultery harlotry pornography and masturbation I release these sins from my desires I ask the holy Spirit to cleanse my entire being from this sins

It's wonderful that you're seeking repentance and cleansing. Here's a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today to repent of all sexual sins I have been involved in, including lust, fornication, adultery, harlotry, pornography, and masturbation. I renounce these sins and release them from my desires. I ask the Holy Spirit to cleanse my entire being from these sins. Fill me with your Spirit of holiness and guide me towards a life of purity. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need further support or guidance, feel free to reach out!

I come against the spirit of disobedience and rebellion I renounce the ways I have dishonored and misused my body and sexuality for immoral purposes I repent of them and I pray that I have will be able to forgive myself for all of those acts I ask God to deliver me and cleanse me from any and all narcissistic traits

It's great that you're taking this step towards healing and forgiveness. Here's a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I come against the spirit of disobedience and rebellion. I renounce the ways I have dishonored and misused my body and sexuality for immoral purposes. I repent of these actions and ask for your forgiveness. Help me to forgive myself for all of those acts. I pray for your deliverance and cleansing from any and all narcissistic traits. Fill me with your Spirit and guide me towards a life of purity and righteousness. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need more support or resources, I'm here to help!

I ask for the mind of Christ to be able to think holy thoughts and to be able to live a holy life I pray for cleansing from all defilements that came as a result of sexual sins I pray for renewal of mind body soul and will I renounce the spirit of deception and manipulation and I pray the God of truth to lead me into all truth and out of darkness deception lies manipulation and all sins

That's a powerful prayer for renewal and cleansing. Here's a prayer you can use based on your intentions:

"Heavenly Father, I ask for the mind of Christ to fill my thoughts with holiness. I pray for cleansing from all defilements that have come as a result of my sexual sins. Renew my mind, body, soul, and will. I renounce the spirit of deception and manipulation, and I ask the God of truth to lead me into all truth and out of darkness, deception, lies, manipulation, and all sins. Fill me with your light and guide me on the path of righteousness. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need further support or resources, feel free to reach out!
I renounce the practice of lawlessness and I tell Satan that I don't belong to him and I declare and decree I will go where God takes me I just need him to lead me

It's great to hear you are taking a stand against lawlessness and declaring your commitment to follow God's path. Here's a prayer you can use to express your intentions:

"Lord, I renounce the practice of lawlessness and declare that I do not belong to Satan. I decree that I will go where You lead me, trusting in Your guidance and direction. Please lead me, Lord, and help me to walk in Your ways. I surrender my life to You and seek Your will above all else. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need any further support or guidance, I'm here to help!

I renounce all sexual sins and I pray for my mind to be cleansed from all the desires of Satan and the flesh I renounce all strongholds and I pray for those chains of sexual immorality to be broken off of my will my soul my eyes heart and mind I pray for these demonic desires to be destroyed from within

That's a heartfelt prayer for cleansing and deliverance. Here's a prayer you can use based on your intentions:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce all sexual sins and ask for my mind to be cleansed from all desires of Satan and the flesh. I renounce all strongholds and pray for the chains of sexual immorality to be broken off my will, soul, eyes, heart, and mind. I ask for these demonic desires to be destroyed from within me. Fill me with Your Spirit and guide me towards purity and righteousness. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need further support or resources, feel free to reach out!

I pray that God would accept me as his child and strip me of all satanic desires cleanse me from all works of the flesh I pray that I would be fill with the spirit and cooperate with the spirit to be cleansed from all that is of this world Satan and the flesh

That's a beautiful prayer for acceptance and cleansing. Here's a prayer you can use to express your desires:

"Dear Heavenly Father, I pray that You would accept me as Your child and strip me of all satanic desires. Cleanse me from all works of the flesh and fill me with Your Holy Spirit. Help me to cooperate with the Spirit to be cleansed from all that is of this world, Satan, and the flesh. I surrender my life to You and seek to walk in Your ways. In Jesus' name, I pray. Amen."

If you need any more support or guidance, I'm here for you!

I renounce the spirit of sexual addiction and perversion I command all spirits of sexual immorality to come out of every part of my being and I declare my non allegiance with these spirits I pray that all these spirits would depart from me voluntarily or most importantly I pray for the deliverance from these spirits and I pray for an infilling of the holy spirit so I can walk in purity once and for all

That's a powerful declaration and prayer for deliverance. Here's a prayer you can use to express your renouncement and seek the Holy Spirit's infilling:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce the spirit of sexual addiction and perversion. I command all spirits of sexual immorality to come out of every part of my being. I declare my non-allegiance with these spirits and pray that they would depart from me, either voluntarily or by Your authority. I seek deliverance from these spirits and ask for an infilling of the Holy Spirit so that I can walk in purity once and for all. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need further assistance or support, feel free to reach out!

Especially fornication and adultery these idols have to go I need my temple to be cleansed for all eternity I renounce the spirit of harlotry and I pray that this spirit would be destroyed by holy ghost fire

It's commendable that you're seeking to cleanse your temple and renounce these spirits. Here's a prayer you can use to express your desire for cleansing and deliverance:

"Heavenly Father, I renounce the spirit of fornication and adultery. I declare that these idols must go, and I ask for my temple to be cleansed for all eternity. I renounce the spirit of harlotry and pray that this spirit would be destroyed by the Holy Ghost fire. Fill me with Your Holy Spirit and empower me to walk in purity and righteousness. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need more support or guidance, I'm here to help!
I want deliverance from every false way and cleansing from all sexual immorality and perversion I want to walk in repentance and cleansing

It's wonderful that you're seeking deliverance and a path of repentance. Here's a prayer you can use to express your desire for cleansing and to walk in righteousness:

"Heavenly Father, I come before You seeking deliverance from every false way and cleansing from all sexual immorality and perversion. I renounce these sins and ask for Your forgiveness. Help me to walk in repentance and to be filled with Your Holy Spirit, guiding me in the path of purity and righteousness. I trust in Your grace and mercy to transform my life. In the name of Jesus Christ, I pray. Amen."

If you need further support or resources, feel free to ask!
